The distributed research journal
Usage:
  ReChain [OPTION...]

  -h, --help                Display this usage message
  -v, --version             Display version information
  -p, --publish <path>      Publish a document
  -c, --check               Validate the blockchain
  -m, --mine                Mine a block
  -s, --sign <path>         Sign a published document
      --private_key <path>  Make a private key active
      --public_key <path>   Make a public key active
  -l, --list                List published documents
      --verbose             All logging output
      --silent              No logging output

